last_episode_to_air.name: The horror of the Jinn - Part 1
last_episode_to_air.overview: Aamna's life is one of misery as she feels trapped in a childless marriage and faces constant derision from her mother-in-law. But everything changes when she encounters a Jinn in an abandoned house who grants her the wish of motherhood. But little does she know that the Jinn has a sinister intent. What will happen next?
